# Docs/status/round-summaries/

Per-round / per-session deliverables that are too long for direct CHANGELOG
inclusion but must be preserved in canonical archival form.

Naming convention:
  - `AUTONOMOUS_SESSION_REPORT_<YYYY-MM-DD>-<descriptor>.md`
  - `ROUND<N>_SESSION_SUMMARY.txt` (one per autonomous round)
  - `<TOPIC>_SESSION_STATUS.txt` (executive ad-hoc summaries)

These files are loaded into git history but are not the canonical pillar-
status source. The canonical sources for pillar status are:
`TOE-FACT-SHEET.md`, individual `Docs/math/TECT-Math<NN>-*.tex.txt`
notes, and `CHANGELOG.md`. See `Docs/policy/UPDATE_POLICY.md` §14.3
canonical-source hierarchy.
